name: Deflationary (DEF)
description: DEF is the native utility token for the DEFswap Finance platform. DEF is a true deflationary token with a use case and a goal of creating financial literacy. DEF tokens can also be used to purchase DEF NFTs directly from the NFT store. Converting DEF token into fiat is not required before making online purchases at most retail platforms like Shopify and more. Inflation is a lifetime problem and $DEF has a lifetime deflationary solution.
